### Pi-top Battery Reader



Will install to /opt/pi-top-battery-sys

And get battery status every 5 minutes, via a systemd timer script, placing this data into:

`/opt/pi-top-battery-sys/BAT0/uevent`


Will also build and install a lxpanel plugin for the battery status for the 'new' path.


